urney-of-the-brave-300194315.html |title=From Universal Pictures Home Entertainment: The Land Before Time: Journey of the Brave |date=December 17, 2015 |accessdate=February 1, 2016 |publisher=PR Newswire |author=Universal Pictures Home Entertainment}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Range 15]]''\n| President\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Three Days in August]]''\n| John\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Bigger Fatter Liar]]''\n| Larry Wolf\n| Direct-to-video<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.kusi.com/story/34454732/from-universal-pictures-home-entertainment-ricky-garcia-and-barry-bostwick-go-head-to-head-in-the-all-new-side-splitting-comedy-bigger-fatter-liar |title=From Universal Pictures Home Entertainment: Ricky Garcia And Barry Bostwick Go Head To Head In The All-New Side-Splitting Comedy Bigger Fatter Liar |publisher=Universal Pictures Home Entertainment |via=[[KUSI]] |date=February 8, 2017 |access-date=February 9, 2017 |url-status = dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075230/http://www.kusi.com/story/34454732/from-universal-pictures-home-entertainment-ricky-garcia-and-barry-bostwick-go-head-to-head-in-the-all-new-side-splitting-comedy-bigger-fatter-liar |archivedate=February 11, 2017 |df= }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| ''[[Incredibles 2]]''\n| Mayor\n| Voice role<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/incredibles-2-review-holly-hunter-1202837069/r |title=Film Review: \u2018Incredibles 2\u2019 |publisher=Variety |date=June 11, 2018 |access-date=June 13, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Santa Girl''\n| Santa Claus\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| ''Grand-Daddy Day Care''\n| Dynamite Dan North\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Undercover Brother 2]]''\n| The Man\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[American Pie Presents: Girls' Rules]]''\n| PeePaw\n|\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Murder by Natural Causes]]''\n| Gil Weston\n| Television film\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[You Can't Take It with You (play)#Film and TV adaptations|Y